- Health check latency should be in seconds (Prometheus convention)
- PROXY_HEALTH gauge should be updated on every check, not just on change
- Failover metric can be used to count both failovers and failbacks (direction is in labels)
- Consider adding a startup metric to mark when health checks began

## Acceptance Criteria

- Health check results update metrics correctly
- Proxy health gauge reflects current health state
- Latency histogram populated with reasonable values
- Failover counter increments on failover/failback events
